org.apache.drill.exec.store.parquet

Class BaseParquetMetadataProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.exec.store.parquet.BaseParquetMetadataProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParquetMetadataProvider, TableMetadataProvider
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HiveParquetTableMetadataProvider, ParquetTableMetadataProviderImpl

    public abstract class BaseParquetMetadataProvider
extends Object
implements ParquetMetadataProvider
    Implementation of ParquetMetadataProvider which contains base methods for obtaining metadata from parquet statistics.
